sentence: A look at the weighted underlying holdings of the WisdomTree LargeCap Dividend Fund (Symbol: DLN) shows an impressive 13.7% of holdings on a weighted basis have experienced insider buying within the past six months.

Home Depot Inc (Symbol: HD), which makes up 0.95% of the WisdomTree LargeCap Dividend Fund (Symbol: DLN), has seen 2 directors and officers purchase shares in the past six months, according to the recent Form 4 data.
The ETF holds a total of $18,216,164 worth of HD, making it the #23 largest holding.
